### 3. CREATE BLOGS (Linked to each user)

### Alice's Blog
POST {{baseUrl}}/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.token}}

{
  "title": "React Best Practices 2026",
  "author": "Alice Tan",
  "url": "https://react.dev",
  "likes": 15
}

